    dc:description "FIGURE 4. A. Lateral thoracic region of Thevenetimyia spinosavus Maass & Bertone, sp. nov. showing pleural pollinosity and setae, as well as the diagnostic spine-like scutellar tubercles (black arrow). B. Close-up of scutellar tubercles." ;
